headline: Elavon launches fresh logo and bold new look for a dynamic 2026
summary: ATLANTA, February 09, 2026--Elavon, a wholly owned subsidiary of U.S. Bank and one of the largest payments processors globally, is strategically evolving its brand identify to better align with the modern customer journey, showcasing the company's evolution in the competitive payments solutions landscape.
